WEBVTT

01:27.490 --> 01:31.940
[The Dark Romance]

01:32.150 --> 01:34.900
[Episode 5]

01:41.710 --> 01:47.270
[Guangzhong Road Exit]

01:42.870 --> 01:43.729
Hello, Ms. Yan.

01:47.460 --> 01:52.710
[Good News]

01:52.820 --> 01:54.370
[2019 Faculty Series
of Higher Education Institutions]

01:54.400 --> 01:58.200
[Public Notice: Senior Professional Title
Successful Candidates]

02:01.150 --> 02:01.680
Yan Ling.

02:06.430 --> 02:08.560
I was looking through the list just now

02:08.680 --> 02:10.280
and couldn't find your name.

02:10.280 --> 02:11.710
This is so unfair.

02:13.000 --> 02:14.190
I got a penalty,

02:14.470 --> 02:16.560
so my professional title review
didn't get approved.

02:16.560 --> 02:17.820
It's understandable.

02:18.079 --> 02:19.430
Besides, the university

02:19.430 --> 02:20.310
has to give

02:20.840 --> 02:23.170
an explanation to other faculty members.

02:23.710 --> 02:25.460
You help others all day long,

02:25.560 --> 02:26.360
and what's the result?

02:26.360 --> 02:28.090
You ended up hurting yourself.

02:29.310 --> 02:30.570
It's not that serious.

02:31.000 --> 02:31.560
You

02:31.390 --> 02:36.370
[Good News]

02:31.710 --> 02:33.510
just don't know the priorities.

02:34.030 --> 02:35.120
What if not getting
the senior professional title

02:35.120 --> 02:36.780
affects your reappointment?

02:43.170 --> 02:44.910
[2019 Faculty Series
of Higher Education Institutions]

02:44.940 --> 02:47.140
[Public Notice: Senior Professional Title
Successful Candidates]

02:49.150 --> 02:50.240
I've verified
Xia Yi's passport information

02:50.240 --> 02:52.840
with
the Entry-Exit Administration Department.

02:52.840 --> 02:53.520
It's real.

02:56.630 --> 02:58.960
Who is the one
you asked me about last time,

02:59.400 --> 03:00.560
the one at the beach?

03:04.630 --> 03:06.160
I will keep looking into it.

03:09.880 --> 03:15.660
[Call History]

03:17.470 --> 03:18.120
Leilei,

03:19.430 --> 03:21.430
what exactly did you want to tell me?

03:22.710 --> 03:24.030
Just to say goodbye?

03:59.470 --> 04:00.470
Morning, Dr. Luo.

04:00.560 --> 04:01.090
Morning.

04:01.910 --> 04:02.750
Have you had breakfast?

04:02.750 --> 04:03.630
Yes. You?

04:03.840 --> 04:04.360
Me too.

04:05.190 --> 04:05.520
Well,

04:05.560 --> 04:07.190
there's an academic seminar next month.

04:06.220 --> 04:08.850
[Incoming Call]

04:07.190 --> 04:07.990
Are you going?

04:08.400 --> 04:09.080
When is it?

04:09.240 --> 04:10.500
The 18th of next month.

04:10.590 --> 04:12.150
I asked the nurse to put the invitation

04:12.150 --> 04:13.200
on your desk.

04:13.840 --> 04:14.360
No problem.

04:14.360 --> 04:15.120
I'll go up and take a look.

04:15.120 --> 04:15.450
Okay.

04:15.840 --> 04:19.820
[International Medical Center]

04:17.310 --> 04:18.070
Morning, Dr. Luo.

04:18.070 --> 04:18.600
Morning.

04:19.630 --> 04:20.430
Hello, Dr. Luo.

04:19.870 --> 04:22.320
[Lihai Renxin Hospital]

04:20.560 --> 04:20.920
Hello, Dr. Luo.

04:20.920 --> 04:21.450
Morning.

04:22.950 --> 04:23.950
Morning, Dr. Luo.

04:24.240 --> 04:24.770
Morning.

04:26.070 --> 04:26.740
Fu,

04:26.800 --> 04:28.810
give me some blank medical records.

04:29.000 --> 04:29.360
Okay.

04:32.710 --> 04:34.130
[Smile Service, Warm as Always]

04:39.409 --> 04:47.480
[Smile Service, Warm as Always]

04:51.430 --> 04:52.750
Didn't I tell you

04:53.630 --> 04:54.960
not to call me casually?

05:26.010 --> 05:28.860
[Smile Service, Warm as Always]

05:59.120 --> 05:59.920
What's wrong?

06:03.160 --> 06:04.390
Are you okay, Dr. Luo?

06:05.070 --> 06:05.630
I'm fine.

06:06.800 --> 06:08.460
I just bumped into something.

06:09.040 --> 06:10.270
There aren't that many VIP patients.

06:10.270 --> 06:11.480
No need to rush.

06:21.600 --> 06:24.130
Let's grab dinner together
after work today.

06:27.430 --> 06:28.290
Did you forget?

06:28.360 --> 06:30.760
I'm on the night shift today.
It's Tuesday.

06:31.070 --> 06:31.560
How about...

06:31.560 --> 06:31.870
Never mind.

06:31.870 --> 06:32.750
I'll ask Jiang to swap with...

06:32.750 --> 06:34.150
That's too much trouble.

06:38.159 --> 06:39.490
It's about time, right?

06:39.730 --> 06:40.860
Call the patient in.

06:58.390 --> 06:59.510
Sorry, I've really
never seen anything like this.

06:58.570 --> 07:03.030
[Lihai Tattoo Forum]

06:59.510 --> 07:00.830
Free design, free tattoo.

07:00.830 --> 07:01.830
DM if interested.

07:01.830 --> 07:03.430
I am a design major graduate,

07:03.510 --> 07:04.510
with solid basic skills,

07:04.510 --> 07:06.190
urgently seeking models
to build my tattoo portfolio.

07:06.190 --> 07:07.840
All posted works can be tattooed.

07:07.840 --> 07:09.190
Completely free of charge.

07:09.190 --> 07:10.680
DM if interested.

07:11.820 --> 07:14.110
[Dr. Luo Liang]

07:16.830 --> 07:18.020
Hello, Dr. Luo.

07:18.310 --> 07:18.830
Ms. Yan.

07:20.190 --> 07:21.430
Are you free tonight?

07:22.040 --> 07:24.800
We didn't get together after you came back
from your hometown last time.

07:24.800 --> 07:26.600
A restaurant just opened today.

07:26.800 --> 07:28.600
Do you want to go try it together?

07:29.390 --> 07:31.500
Today is Tuesday.

07:31.680 --> 07:33.190
You are going to reject me again?

07:33.190 --> 07:33.800
No.

07:33.800 --> 07:34.360
Okay.

07:35.000 --> 07:36.400
I understand. I'm sorry.

07:36.560 --> 07:37.420
I bothered you.

07:37.490 --> 07:38.290
No, no, no.

07:39.560 --> 07:40.690
You misunderstood.

07:41.950 --> 07:42.500
Okay.

07:42.720 --> 07:43.950
Tonight is fine.

07:45.070 --> 07:45.600
Great.

07:46.190 --> 07:47.460
At 6:30 tonight.

07:47.510 --> 07:49.560
I'll send you the address
of the restaurant.

07:49.560 --> 07:50.140
Okay.

08:00.870 --> 08:01.400
Goodbye.

08:02.070 --> 08:02.600
Jiale.

08:08.530 --> 08:11.730
Jiale, I will drop you off
at the programming class later.

08:11.920 --> 08:13.850
Your dad will pick you up
when you are done.

08:13.850 --> 08:14.710
What about you?

08:15.190 --> 08:17.250
I'm going to have dinner with Dr. Luo.

08:17.310 --> 08:18.360
Dr. Luo?

08:19.520 --> 08:20.690
He's quite nice.

08:23.390 --> 08:24.040
Mom.

08:25.190 --> 08:26.660
I think you should wear

08:26.830 --> 08:29.510
the dress Godmother gave you.

08:30.360 --> 08:31.440
It's still new.

08:31.950 --> 08:33.480
I've never seen you wear it.

08:34.600 --> 08:36.260
What's wrong with my clothes?

08:36.960 --> 08:37.760
Isn't it good?

08:38.150 --> 08:39.880
You look like a female teacher.

08:41.720 --> 08:43.320
I am a female teacher anyway.

08:44.320 --> 08:45.600
Anyway, I think

08:45.600 --> 08:47.800
you'll definitely look better in that.

09:02.240 --> 09:02.970
You are here.

09:04.720 --> 09:05.850
Give your bag to him.

09:07.720 --> 09:08.580
Let me help you.

09:09.000 --> 09:09.670
Thank you.

09:09.870 --> 09:10.800
Please sit down.

09:20.790 --> 09:22.000
Do you want to drink a little?

09:22.000 --> 09:22.480
No.

09:22.600 --> 09:23.830
I drove today.

09:24.200 --> 09:24.930
Have a drink.

09:25.790 --> 09:26.970
I know you can drink.

09:27.360 --> 09:29.550
You can call a designated driver
after drinking.

09:29.550 --> 09:30.880
Just to keep me company.

09:32.670 --> 09:33.330
Okay.

09:52.200 --> 09:53.240
Are you okay?

09:59.000 --> 09:59.630
I'm fine.

10:01.360 --> 10:02.760
It's just that suddenly,

10:03.840 --> 10:05.300
I really wanted to see you.

10:11.360 --> 10:12.890
I received a message today.

10:13.550 --> 10:14.810
My father passed away.

10:23.240 --> 10:25.370
He had been disabled for so many years.

10:26.070 --> 10:27.240
For this day,

10:27.480 --> 10:29.410
I had long been mentally prepared.

10:31.440 --> 10:32.700
As a doctor,

10:33.790 --> 10:35.990
I have seen so many partings and deaths.

10:37.840 --> 10:40.030
But when it really happens to me,

10:42.120 --> 10:42.910
I still...

10:49.910 --> 10:51.040
He was very serious.

10:52.200 --> 10:53.720
I rarely saw him smile.

10:55.390 --> 10:56.850
He was also very talented,

10:57.390 --> 10:59.720
but unfortunately born at the wrong time.

11:00.290 --> 11:01.520
He went from a student

11:02.150 --> 11:03.080
to a farmer.

11:04.200 --> 11:06.000
Axes and chainsaws

11:07.120 --> 11:08.180
replaced his pens.

11:10.390 --> 11:12.030
Later, a falling tree

11:12.840 --> 11:13.720
broke his leg.

11:16.270 --> 11:17.580
Get a car!

11:18.150 --> 11:19.050
Watch his legs!

11:25.500 --> 11:27.250
The only time I saw him smile

11:28.840 --> 11:31.300
was probably
when I got into medical school.

11:41.310 --> 11:42.370
Do you think...

11:45.070 --> 11:46.670
I look vulnerable like this?

11:49.360 --> 11:49.960
No.

11:50.360 --> 11:50.960
No.

11:56.170 --> 11:57.830
Actually, in our line of work,

11:59.180 --> 11:59.980
it's very sad.

12:03.030 --> 12:04.000
We constantly

12:04.550 --> 12:07.150
deal with other people's
emotional problems,

12:08.560 --> 12:09.820
but it's hard for us...

12:13.270 --> 12:14.960
to get comfort from others.

12:18.150 --> 12:19.720
Thank you for trusting me

12:21.360 --> 12:22.490
and telling me this.

12:24.480 --> 12:25.320
I understand.

12:26.630 --> 12:27.760
I know what you mean.

12:28.750 --> 12:29.870
I understand.

12:31.240 --> 12:32.970
The moment I got the news today,

12:35.870 --> 12:37.320
I just wanted to call you.

12:49.760 --> 12:50.360
Excuse me.

12:53.870 --> 12:54.800
Enjoy your meal.

12:56.120 --> 12:57.780
You should eat something too.

12:58.120 --> 12:59.520
I asked you out for dinner

12:59.540 --> 13:01.400
and told you so many sad things,

13:01.420 --> 13:02.750
ruining your appetite.

13:03.240 --> 13:04.840
It makes me feel very guilty.

13:24.840 --> 13:25.640
What's wrong?

13:34.270 --> 13:36.000
My father passed away too.

13:40.680 --> 13:42.130
When I was 14.

14:04.550 --> 14:05.390
They say

14:06.480 --> 14:07.880
if you share your sorrow,

14:09.040 --> 14:10.240
it's reduced by half.

14:13.840 --> 14:14.750
Thank you

14:16.400 --> 14:18.200
for keeping me company tonight.

14:18.840 --> 14:19.770
My condolences.

14:20.200 --> 14:20.840
Take care.

14:22.460 --> 14:24.030
If you ever feel sad—

14:24.030 --> 14:25.120
I'll call you.

14:33.630 --> 14:35.230
Let me know when you get home.

14:53.050 --> 14:54.730
[Wuzhou City]

15:52.180 --> 15:55.050
[Dismantle]

15:55.980 --> 15:57.530
[Dismantle]

17:22.960 --> 17:23.490
Get lost!

17:30.510 --> 17:31.350
Pick it up.

17:34.480 --> 17:35.210
Are you deaf?

17:49.000 --> 17:50.000
You're back.

17:51.050 --> 17:52.850
You didn't even tell me earlier.

17:57.590 --> 17:58.530
Have you eaten?

17:59.790 --> 18:00.440
Not yet.

18:01.550 --> 18:02.160
And you?

18:03.200 --> 18:04.330
I brought some back.

18:04.400 --> 18:07.060
You're eating someone else's
leftovers again.

18:09.310 --> 18:10.420
It's untouched.

18:11.640 --> 18:13.640
Don't I send money back every month?

18:14.270 --> 18:16.070
Why do you have to live like this?

18:19.350 --> 18:20.070
He's dead.

18:21.830 --> 18:22.680
Are you happy?

18:33.550 --> 18:34.750
He got off too easily.

18:43.480 --> 18:43.960
Here,

18:44.440 --> 18:45.640
eat it while it's hot.

18:47.000 --> 18:47.660
You eat too.

18:48.750 --> 18:49.240
Eat.

19:12.430 --> 19:13.040
Eat.

19:20.590 --> 19:21.690
The funeral

19:22.160 --> 19:23.520
will cost money too.

19:24.000 --> 19:24.440
I know.

19:27.210 --> 19:27.920
And...

19:31.000 --> 19:31.990
your sister...

19:32.270 --> 19:33.400
Why bring her up?

19:40.110 --> 19:41.550
If she hears the news,

19:42.000 --> 19:43.730
she will definitely come home.

19:48.200 --> 19:50.200
I'll arrange the cremation tomorrow.

19:50.200 --> 19:52.260
Forget about the farewell ceremony.

19:52.350 --> 19:54.410
I'll also hurry up with the cemetery.

19:55.880 --> 19:56.510
Okay.

19:58.720 --> 19:59.200
Okay.

20:14.400 --> 20:16.030
You are just a little brat!

20:16.070 --> 20:16.880
Day after day,

20:16.960 --> 20:18.360
all you do is drag me down!

20:18.720 --> 20:19.660
And you,

20:20.750 --> 20:21.900
just like your mom,

20:22.000 --> 20:22.960
shameless!

20:22.960 --> 20:23.750
My whole life

20:24.000 --> 20:25.910
has been ruined by you two!

20:26.110 --> 20:27.650
If it weren't for you two,

20:28.200 --> 20:30.440
I would have returned
to the city long ago.

20:30.440 --> 20:31.700
It's all your fault!

20:32.720 --> 20:34.400
You're always trying to seduce me!

20:34.400 --> 20:36.200
I will beat you to death today!

20:36.310 --> 20:36.880
Get lost!

20:37.270 --> 20:37.800
Get lost!

20:37.870 --> 20:39.510
Don't let me see you again!

20:53.880 --> 20:54.280
Hello,

20:54.480 --> 20:54.920
Mom.

20:55.440 --> 20:56.960
How is your work lately?

20:58.920 --> 20:59.880
Pretty good.

21:00.590 --> 21:02.720
You've been a lecturer for 4 or 5 years.

21:02.790 --> 21:04.960
Should you get promoted
to associate professor?

21:04.960 --> 21:06.290
Did you apply this year?

21:07.830 --> 21:09.560
It'll be a while longer.

21:09.750 --> 21:10.960
Keep lying.

21:11.200 --> 21:13.000
You never tell me the truth.

21:13.030 --> 21:15.160
I've looked through the public list

21:15.160 --> 21:16.160
on your university's website.

21:16.160 --> 21:17.420
You're not on it at all.

21:17.720 --> 21:19.070
Universities nowadays have

21:19.070 --> 21:20.750
the "up or out" policy.

21:21.110 --> 21:22.710
What are you going to do next?

21:22.720 --> 21:24.110
If you don't get promoted this year,

21:24.110 --> 21:25.640
you'll be fired.

21:27.720 --> 21:29.070
It's not that serious.

21:30.030 --> 21:32.230
Our university doesn't have that rule.

21:32.430 --> 21:33.720
You're no longer on your own,

21:33.720 --> 21:34.640
with no one else to feed.

21:34.640 --> 21:35.840
You still have Jiale.

21:36.200 --> 21:37.630
When you got pregnant,
you insisted on having him,

21:37.630 --> 21:39.070
claiming you could raise him.

21:39.070 --> 21:39.640
And now?

21:40.110 --> 21:40.640
How are you going to raise him?

21:40.640 --> 21:42.480
You just do whatever you want,

21:42.480 --> 21:43.400
just like when you were little.

21:43.400 --> 21:44.350
You only think about yourself.

21:44.350 --> 21:45.880
You never consider others.

21:45.920 --> 21:46.780
Let me tell you,

21:46.860 --> 21:47.790
this isn't over.

21:48.000 --> 21:49.860
Think carefully about what to do.

22:12.160 --> 22:13.910
[Dr. Luo Liang]

22:14.240 --> 22:15.610
[Are you busy?]

22:15.630 --> 22:18.110
[It's okay. Call me when you're done.]

22:18.130 --> 22:19.850
[No hurry.]

22:40.800 --> 22:42.120
[Yan Ling]

22:51.270 --> 22:51.790
Hello.

22:53.110 --> 22:53.590
Hello.

22:55.200 --> 22:55.930
Are you okay?

22:57.350 --> 22:58.500
I was just worried

22:59.110 --> 23:01.840
that I brought up
some sad memories the other day.

23:02.640 --> 23:03.260
I'm sorry.

23:04.790 --> 23:06.510
No, I'm fine.

23:08.110 --> 23:08.970
What about you?

23:09.880 --> 23:12.110
Did everything go smoothly
after you went back?

23:12.110 --> 23:12.770
It was okay.

23:14.240 --> 23:16.440
I arranged the cremation for tomorrow.

23:16.830 --> 23:17.960
But my mom...

23:19.200 --> 23:21.400
has been vomiting and having diarrhea.

23:22.110 --> 23:23.570
I took her to the hospital,

23:24.350 --> 23:25.750
and she just stabilized.

23:26.960 --> 23:28.240
Is your mom okay?

23:29.070 --> 23:31.350
She's actually always been in good health.

23:31.350 --> 23:33.030
It's probably a physical reaction

23:33.030 --> 23:34.440
caused by her emotions.

23:36.880 --> 23:38.110
The other day,

23:39.640 --> 23:41.350
you suddenly felt sick and threw up.

23:41.350 --> 23:43.350
You must have been very sad too.

23:47.030 --> 23:48.480
Could you please teach me

23:50.500 --> 23:51.830
how to get through this?

23:54.750 --> 23:56.810
I might not be qualified to teach you.

24:12.310 --> 24:13.660
I would recall...

24:17.000 --> 24:18.930
By holding onto the best memories,

24:20.130 --> 24:21.270
in my heart,

24:24.000 --> 24:25.800
it seems as if he were still here.

24:34.860 --> 24:36.510
Uncle, is there a letter for me today?

24:36.510 --> 24:37.140
Yes.

24:37.540 --> 24:39.680
[For my beloved Ling]

24:38.110 --> 24:39.320
I would repeatedly

24:39.760 --> 24:41.490
read the letters he wrote to me.

24:43.270 --> 24:43.960
My dad

24:46.200 --> 24:47.860
would talk to me about the sea.

24:49.940 --> 24:51.140
He told me

24:52.400 --> 24:54.000
smearing engine oil on your face

24:54.000 --> 24:55.240
can prevent sunburn

24:56.790 --> 24:58.720
and that if there's no fresh water,

24:59.110 --> 25:00.770
eating fish can replenish it.

25:01.750 --> 25:02.910
He would teach me

25:03.310 --> 25:04.910
how to identify directions.

25:06.790 --> 25:07.970
Dad said

25:09.200 --> 25:11.600
point the hour hand of your watch
at the sun,

25:13.000 --> 25:14.590
and the bisector of the acute angle

25:14.590 --> 25:17.320
between the hour hand
and the 12 o'clock position

25:17.830 --> 25:18.880
points south.

25:21.480 --> 25:23.110
Come on, hold on, baby.

25:24.000 --> 25:25.200
Dad would teach me

25:26.750 --> 25:28.340
how to avoid storms.

25:29.440 --> 25:30.320
Be brave,

25:30.550 --> 25:33.010
and even the biggest storm
can be conquered.

25:33.680 --> 25:35.030
He said no matter how big

25:35.830 --> 25:37.290
or dangerous the storm is,

25:37.880 --> 25:39.080
you must never give up

25:41.030 --> 25:42.590
or let go of the helm.

25:44.550 --> 25:45.680
He really was

25:47.680 --> 25:48.680
a great father.

25:50.440 --> 25:51.790
Did he work at sea?

25:54.200 --> 25:56.460
He was the captain of an ocean freighter.

25:57.880 --> 25:58.930
So he

26:00.640 --> 26:01.970
died in the line of duty?

26:04.240 --> 26:04.880
No.

26:08.000 --> 26:09.500
During a family visit,

26:11.000 --> 26:12.220
he had an accident.

26:21.920 --> 26:23.170
I originally thought

26:24.310 --> 26:26.310
I could recover and move on quickly.

26:28.550 --> 26:29.550
But it doesn't feel

26:29.550 --> 26:30.490
realistic.

26:31.880 --> 26:32.540
Look at you,

26:34.440 --> 26:35.680
it's been so long,

26:36.750 --> 26:38.610
and it seems you haven't moved on.

26:42.480 --> 26:43.820
I'm so sorry.

26:45.720 --> 26:47.400
I was supposed to comfort you,

26:48.510 --> 26:50.510
but I ended up doing all the talking.

26:52.920 --> 26:53.560
Not at all.

26:54.880 --> 26:55.810
Thank you so much

26:57.200 --> 26:58.800
for sharing all this with me.

27:01.440 --> 27:04.240
Getting through it
by holding onto good memories.

27:06.350 --> 27:07.880
I've learned how to do that.

27:09.880 --> 27:10.880
You know what?

27:13.480 --> 27:14.510
Before this,

27:17.270 --> 27:19.670
I've never told anyone about these things.

27:22.480 --> 27:24.010
Then you must have been a kid

27:24.510 --> 27:26.640
who was very sensible from a young age.

27:27.240 --> 27:29.240
With such deep sorrow in your heart,

27:29.680 --> 27:31.540
you didn't share it with your mom.

27:32.240 --> 27:33.590
You must have been very afraid

27:33.590 --> 27:35.650
of breaking your mom's heart, right?

27:38.160 --> 27:39.390
You and your mother

27:40.590 --> 27:42.790
have depended on each other all the way.

27:43.240 --> 27:44.900
It must have been really hard.

27:50.200 --> 27:50.720
Dad.

28:04.200 --> 28:04.680
Hello?

28:07.390 --> 28:08.520
Are you still there?

28:13.270 --> 28:13.960
Yes.

28:16.190 --> 28:17.330
I'm sorry.

28:18.070 --> 28:18.510
I...

28:18.510 --> 28:19.590
I just got

28:19.590 --> 28:20.440
a work WeChat message.

28:20.440 --> 28:21.840
I have to get back to work.

28:24.030 --> 28:24.590
Sure.

28:25.400 --> 28:27.130
I should be the one apologizing

28:28.000 --> 28:29.330
for taking up your time.

28:30.310 --> 28:31.120
No, not at all.

28:32.720 --> 28:34.170
Take good care of your mom

28:34.680 --> 28:35.800
and yourself.

28:37.440 --> 28:38.090
I will.

28:40.000 --> 28:40.690
You too.

28:41.590 --> 28:42.160
Goodbye.

29:52.400 --> 29:53.330
Family members.

29:55.440 --> 29:56.010
Let me.

29:57.920 --> 29:58.850
My condolences.

30:09.030 --> 30:09.720
I'll call you a car.

30:09.720 --> 30:10.720
You go back first.

30:11.030 --> 30:11.890
What about you?

30:14.680 --> 30:16.710
I'll go find a better box,

30:17.400 --> 30:18.550
then go to the cemetery in advance

30:18.550 --> 30:19.810
to make arrangements.

30:34.880 --> 30:35.450
Hello.

30:35.510 --> 30:36.910
Feel free to look around.

30:45.830 --> 30:47.140
Let me see that box.

30:47.720 --> 30:48.110
Sure.

30:53.110 --> 30:54.720
This one is made of red sandalwood.

30:54.720 --> 30:55.980
It's quite expensive.

31:01.510 --> 31:02.240
I'll take it.

31:02.590 --> 31:03.000
Sure.

31:13.680 --> 31:15.280
What are your best scissors?

31:16.230 --> 31:16.740
Sir,

31:17.070 --> 31:18.400
take a look at this pair.

31:18.550 --> 31:19.070
This pair

31:19.070 --> 31:20.730
is an original German Jaguar.

31:21.510 --> 31:23.840
It's the most professional and high-end.

31:24.640 --> 31:26.370
We also have Kasho and Sassoon.

31:26.720 --> 31:28.050
Kasho is also very good.

31:28.350 --> 31:30.210
We have their Millennium Series.

31:54.240 --> 31:55.300
Don't move around.

31:55.880 --> 31:57.350
Be careful not to get your ears cut.

31:57.350 --> 31:58.960
You are the smartest in the family.

31:58.960 --> 32:00.090
You must study hard.

32:01.200 --> 32:02.680
I am really studying hard.

32:03.720 --> 32:04.260
Really.

32:05.790 --> 32:07.540
I knew you had it in you.

32:07.790 --> 32:08.840
In my life,

32:09.000 --> 32:10.310
I can only do haircuts for others.

32:10.310 --> 32:11.370
You are different.

32:11.480 --> 32:12.440
You are going to get a PhD,

32:12.440 --> 32:13.070
become a doctor,

32:13.070 --> 32:14.240
and hold a scalpel.

32:14.440 --> 32:16.640
You've been good with your hands
since you were little.

32:16.640 --> 32:19.160
You must go to the best university
in the future.

32:19.160 --> 32:20.200
You'll go to Shenchuan

32:20.200 --> 32:21.130
or Gangdao.

32:21.200 --> 32:22.600
I will earn your tuition.

32:43.000 --> 32:43.880
Dr. Luo

32:44.000 --> 32:45.070
sent me

32:45.070 --> 32:46.070
a WeChat message.

32:46.640 --> 32:47.270
Did he?

32:48.720 --> 32:49.580
What did he say?

32:50.440 --> 32:53.200
He said to thank me
for helping him take care of the hamster

32:53.200 --> 32:55.240
and let you add a chicken leg
to my dinner.

32:55.240 --> 32:57.370
He'll reimburse you when he gets back.

32:58.480 --> 32:59.000
Okay,

32:59.510 --> 33:00.170
no problem.

33:03.870 --> 33:04.400
Alright.

33:05.070 --> 33:05.670
Let me see.

33:07.720 --> 33:08.360
Get up

33:08.440 --> 33:09.700
and look in the mirror.

33:11.070 --> 33:11.730
Take a look.

33:12.550 --> 33:13.350
Do you like it?

33:14.790 --> 33:15.790
It's pretty good.

33:16.500 --> 33:18.160
You've never asked me before

33:18.160 --> 33:19.000
if I liked it.

33:20.790 --> 33:21.500
Really?

33:23.160 --> 33:25.290
Then I'll ask more often in the future.

33:26.440 --> 33:27.770
Shall we take a picture?

33:28.510 --> 33:28.970
Come on.

33:32.330 --> 33:33.140
Smile.

33:34.920 --> 33:35.510
Alright.

33:39.830 --> 33:40.890
Is it Dr. Luo?

33:41.350 --> 33:41.750
No.

33:42.960 --> 33:43.890
Hello, who is it?

34:04.000 --> 34:05.260
What's wrong with you?

34:05.590 --> 34:06.550
What happened?

34:09.159 --> 34:09.560
Hurry.

34:09.960 --> 34:11.090
Get in the car first.

34:20.719 --> 34:22.179
He knew you were pregnant

34:22.199 --> 34:23.929
and still beat you up like this?

34:25.280 --> 34:27.679
How can you forgive him
time and time again?

34:28.190 --> 34:30.850
He's been under a lot of pressure
at work lately.

34:32.320 --> 34:33.850
Don't make excuses for him.

34:34.150 --> 34:36.030
Even if you don't think about yourself,

34:36.030 --> 34:37.960
think about the baby in your belly.

34:46.030 --> 34:47.810
How did you get this tattoo?

34:48.280 --> 34:49.340
Who made you get it?

34:49.670 --> 34:51.400
Was it your husband? Was it him?

34:53.510 --> 34:54.340
It wasn't him.

34:55.760 --> 34:57.360
It has nothing to do with him.

34:57.510 --> 34:59.000
It's all my fault.

34:59.800 --> 35:01.150
I'm a very bad person.

35:01.840 --> 35:03.500
I deserved to be beaten by him.

35:09.670 --> 35:10.700
Before...

35:12.630 --> 35:13.890
I borrowed some money.

35:15.250 --> 35:17.850
But I didn't know
the interest would be so high.

35:18.670 --> 35:19.920
The debt snowballed.

35:20.760 --> 35:22.020
I couldn't pay it back.

35:23.510 --> 35:24.760
So I was forced by the creditors

35:24.760 --> 35:27.540
to get this tattoo as they demanded.

35:28.590 --> 35:30.440
I also took those kinds of photos.

35:30.440 --> 35:33.240
They said taking them
would offset some interest.

35:33.960 --> 35:34.470
You mean

35:35.190 --> 35:35.970
Leilei

35:36.960 --> 35:38.160
took out a naked loan?

35:38.440 --> 35:39.550
So I guess

35:40.440 --> 35:42.050
the tattoo on Leilei

35:42.670 --> 35:43.440
was also done according to

35:43.440 --> 35:45.040
the demands of these people.

35:48.840 --> 35:50.170
How much did you borrow?

35:51.550 --> 35:53.010
The principal was 80,000.

35:53.440 --> 35:55.270
Then I don't know what happened.

35:55.510 --> 35:57.310
The interest just kept rolling,

35:57.760 --> 35:59.710
and it ended up
being hundreds of thousands.

35:59.710 --> 36:01.040
What about your family?

36:01.630 --> 36:02.830
Didn't they help you?

36:06.030 --> 36:08.760
I wasn't in touch with my family
during that time.

36:10.280 --> 36:11.540
My father passed away.

36:13.290 --> 36:14.220
Because of me.

36:16.070 --> 36:16.710
At that time,

36:16.710 --> 36:18.710
I was supposed to be home with my dad,

36:19.190 --> 36:20.920
but I had a fight
with my boyfriend and broke up,

36:20.920 --> 36:22.130
so I ran out.

36:27.150 --> 36:28.670
Then he had a heart attack,

36:28.670 --> 36:29.670
and I wasn't home.

36:31.670 --> 36:32.930
It's all because of me.

36:34.030 --> 36:35.420
I was young

36:35.630 --> 36:36.840
and very ignorant.

36:37.140 --> 36:38.590
If it wasn't for me,

36:38.710 --> 36:40.240
my father wouldn't have...

36:45.290 --> 36:46.160
After that,

36:47.880 --> 36:50.210
my relationship with my mom also went bad.

36:51.510 --> 36:52.710
I knew she blamed me.

36:55.220 --> 36:57.350
And I couldn't forgive myself either.

36:57.980 --> 36:59.540
So I moved out of the house.

37:00.360 --> 37:02.980
Later, my mom was very sad

37:03.090 --> 37:04.420
and immigrated abroad.

37:05.130 --> 37:06.190
Thinking back now,

37:06.190 --> 37:08.070
those years were a living hell.

37:08.070 --> 37:09.590
I did a lot of wrong things,

37:10.670 --> 37:12.270
including borrowing money.

37:16.360 --> 37:17.470
Later on,

37:19.190 --> 37:20.480
I met Liu Ping.

37:22.080 --> 37:24.010
He treated me really, really well.

37:25.190 --> 37:27.520
So I didn't want
to hide anything from him.

37:28.130 --> 37:29.650
After I told him,

37:31.500 --> 37:33.160
he said his heart ached for me,

37:34.900 --> 37:37.540
and then he went and got
the same tattoo as mine.

37:39.670 --> 37:41.670
He said that by getting this tattoo,

37:41.670 --> 37:42.840
it would no longer be

37:42.840 --> 37:44.670
a painful and shameful memory.

37:45.590 --> 37:47.840
It would be a testament to our love.

37:48.960 --> 37:49.660
But...

37:51.920 --> 37:53.150
accepting the way I used to be

37:53.150 --> 37:54.550
might have been too hard.

37:55.030 --> 37:56.700
Every time he got drunk,

37:57.030 --> 37:58.760
he couldn't help but curse at me

37:58.840 --> 37:59.550
and beat me.

38:02.280 --> 38:03.490
I don't blame him at all.

38:03.490 --> 38:04.840
I only blame myself.

38:05.120 --> 38:06.650
I really regret it.

38:06.710 --> 38:07.710
I wish I had never done

38:07.710 --> 38:09.630
those shameful things.

38:09.630 --> 38:12.590
I don't want anyone
to know about these things.

38:17.510 --> 38:18.400
I remember

38:19.070 --> 38:21.110
what you told me about your friend

38:21.630 --> 38:22.550
and her tattoo.

38:24.650 --> 38:26.780
I think she must have regretted it too.

38:28.010 --> 38:30.670
Otherwise,
she wouldn't have made that choice.

38:36.080 --> 38:36.700
Ling.

38:39.830 --> 38:41.570
Will you look down on us?

38:42.650 --> 38:45.050
No, of course not.

38:48.880 --> 38:50.060
So what's next?

38:50.730 --> 38:51.950
Do you have any plans?

38:57.320 --> 38:58.620
If possible,

39:00.400 --> 39:02.340
could you lend me some money?

39:03.100 --> 39:05.900
I want to buy a plane ticket
and hide out for a while.

39:06.740 --> 39:08.990
Because I gave all my money to him.

39:14.540 --> 39:16.510
[Jianan Rd.(S)] [Xingxing Rd]

39:26.230 --> 39:28.140
The friend you mentioned,

39:28.800 --> 39:30.930
I think she must have regretted it too.

39:31.510 --> 39:32.800
She might have been even more regretful

39:32.800 --> 39:34.200
and in more pain than I am.

39:34.230 --> 39:36.790
Otherwise,
she wouldn't have made that choice.

39:36.790 --> 39:38.900
I've made a terrible mistake

39:39.110 --> 39:40.710
that I can't make up for in this lifetime.

39:40.710 --> 39:43.280
I owe you too much.

39:43.550 --> 39:45.280
I will repay you in my next life.

39:45.320 --> 39:47.760
Because you think Godmother
was a bad person

39:47.760 --> 39:49.890
whose mistakes couldn't be forgiven.

39:50.750 --> 39:52.700
Will you look down on us?

39:52.770 --> 39:53.950
[Jianan Rd.(S)] [Xingxing Rd]

40:04.020 --> 40:05.350
I don't blame him at all.

40:05.360 --> 40:06.780
I only blame myself.

40:06.840 --> 40:08.400
I really regret it.

40:08.590 --> 40:09.510
I wish I had never done

40:09.510 --> 40:11.480
those shameful things.

40:11.480 --> 40:14.400
I don't want anyone
to know about these things.

40:14.790 --> 40:17.360
Why did I miss your call?

40:17.100 --> 40:19.010
[Call History]

40:18.070 --> 40:20.330
Why did I fail to save you?

40:30.160 --> 40:32.460
[I am Yan Ling.]

40:35.130 --> 40:35.440
[Yan Ling]

40:35.560 --> 40:38.200
[Sometimes kids' happiness
is really simple.]

40:39.670 --> 40:40.590
A little bit...

40:42.480 --> 40:43.640
A little bit higher.

40:51.710 --> 40:52.440
Ling.

40:52.670 --> 40:53.280
Kexin.

40:55.070 --> 40:56.370
I'll ask you again.

40:56.910 --> 40:58.780
Are you really going to,
because of that past,

40:58.780 --> 41:01.040
let him beat you
for the rest of your life?

41:05.360 --> 41:06.440
I'm not afraid.

41:07.280 --> 41:08.110
But I am afraid

41:08.110 --> 41:10.110
that my child will be beaten like me.

41:12.280 --> 41:14.340
Have you ever thought about changing

41:14.480 --> 41:15.540
and starting over?

41:17.480 --> 41:18.590
You mean

41:19.880 --> 41:20.690
divorce?

41:22.040 --> 41:23.370
I have thought about it.

41:24.480 --> 41:25.320
I have.

41:26.630 --> 41:28.480
Because I don't want my child to grow up

41:28.480 --> 41:30.770
living in fear every day like me.

41:30.790 --> 41:33.480
If you make a mistake,
you should cut your losses in time.

41:33.480 --> 41:36.010
You can't make up for it
with another mistake.

41:36.760 --> 41:38.560
That will only make things worse

41:39.400 --> 41:41.200
and ultimately irretrievable.

41:50.840 --> 41:51.900
My good friend

41:53.400 --> 41:56.000
had no one to help her
during her hardest times,

41:56.480 --> 41:58.960
so she could only make
one mistake after another.

41:58.960 --> 41:59.690
In the end,

42:00.110 --> 42:03.240
she didn't even have the chance
to regret and start over.

42:06.880 --> 42:08.310
Let's not do anything

42:09.880 --> 42:11.400
that we will regret,

42:12.480 --> 42:13.150
okay?

42:20.480 --> 42:21.710
Then what should I do?

42:23.840 --> 42:25.370
I'll help you find a lawyer.

42:26.510 --> 42:27.590
I'm worried

42:28.000 --> 42:30.260
that you won't be able to handle it alone.

42:30.360 --> 42:31.960
You need someone to help you.

42:35.480 --> 42:36.190
Thank you.

42:39.360 --> 42:41.360
I really don't know how to thank you.

42:45.550 --> 42:47.440
I wish we had met earlier.

42:49.590 --> 42:51.450
Let's not talk about this for now.

42:52.070 --> 42:54.150
The most important thing for you right now

42:54.150 --> 42:55.610
is to take care of your body

42:55.710 --> 42:57.440
and keep your emotions stable.

42:58.000 --> 43:00.060
After all, you are eating for two now.

43:04.030 --> 43:05.790
I can raise you by myself,

43:06.030 --> 43:06.550
right?

43:11.960 --> 43:12.630
Thank you.

43:13.760 --> 43:14.550
Thank you.

43:17.720 --> 43:18.400
Don't cry.

43:19.670 --> 43:20.530
It will be okay.

43:21.360 --> 43:22.960
Everything will get better.

43:25.680 --> 43:29.740
[The Dark Romance]

43:34.760 --> 43:35.340
Ma'am,

43:36.000 --> 43:36.990
do you need help?

43:37.190 --> 43:39.000
Grab whatever you want for yourself.

43:39.000 --> 43:40.860
-Thank you. No need.
-Okay, okay.

43:41.960 --> 43:43.960
Changning, you go watch the shop.

43:44.030 --> 43:45.160
I will be right back.

43:45.190 --> 43:45.670
Okay.

43:54.780 --> 43:57.710
[Video 1]

44:00.270 --> 44:01.090
[Daily Necessities, Tobacco,
Wine & Groceries]

44:14.230 --> 44:14.760
Ma'am,

44:15.400 --> 44:16.460
how much are these?

44:17.920 --> 44:21.280
[A Leaf of Loneliness]

44:19.590 --> 44:20.400
Are you okay?

44:21.360 --> 44:22.490
I miss you very much.

44:22.550 --> 44:23.000
Ma'am.

44:23.770 --> 44:24.640
[A Leaf of Loneliness]

44:24.760 --> 44:25.360
Ma'am!

44:26.400 --> 44:27.400
How much are these?
